Through incorporating the gene expression change of the TCGA samples with the CNL on TSGs, we examined the correlation between CNL and TSG gene down-regulation. We utilized the Z-score to assess whether a TSG is up-regulated or down-regulated in specific TCGA samples. Here, Z-score is a transformation of the p value calculated by the formula as below:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
